    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v1 + 0.55) * (v2 + 0.69 * v0 + 0.23)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.08)) + 0.67)
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.46 / tmp + 0.03) * wp.abs(v2 + 0.57)) + wp.cos(0.88))
    v2 = (0.61 / wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.22)))
